Nom nom nom.  Such a cute little place right down the road from us. It was super busy when we arrived for dinner but luckily we didn't have to wait for a table as another couple were just leaving. They also provide the sushi, sushi bowls, and (I think) the onigiri at Berkeley Bowl, which is my go-to for a reasonably-priced lunch / snack.
